  "text": "-Fundamentally the market has to be ready for what you want to do. You may be visionary and you may be ahead of your time but if the market is not ready for it, you're not ready. You can't change the market, the market is always right where it is supposed to be and it's your job as an entrepreneur to cater to the market‖ (Jake). [CITATION_1] .",
